title: Tradgardscafe - Slottstradgarden Ulriksdal
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Buffet, Beer/Wine, European, Swedish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The cafe of a gardening store, situated in the area of Ulriksdal Palace in the National City Park. Offers a vegetarian (with vegan choices) buffet weekdays 11:30am-2pm which consists of main courses, salads, soup, bread, fruits, coffee and tea. The food is made from seasonal, mostly locally and ecologically produced vegetables.
